Description:
   Vigilance is an innate passive alertness shared by all characters at
   some base level. For the Sentinel class, it is a core competency that
   exceeds that of ordinary combatants, granting improved passive awareness
   in all situations. Characters with Vigilance have a reduced chance of
   being surprised, improved detection of hidden enemies, and a better
   chance of acting first when combat initiates unexpectedly.

   For Sentinels, Vigilance is a constant state of operational readiness
   that reflects their role as witnesses and enforcers. They are never
   caught fully off-guard, always maintaining situational awareness even
   while resting. The passive benefit improves base detection, hit, and
   initiative stats at all times.
